    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\u2728 Rare find \u2014 this vehicle is in absolutely mint condition and it shows! From the flawless exterior finish to the spotless, pristine interior, this car presents like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Everything works exactly as it should \u2014 no quirks, no wear, no compromises. If you've been searching for a vehicle you can be truly proud of, your search ends here. Come see it in person and prepare to be impressed!",
