    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\udcbc $6,000 - A budget-conscious buyer's project opportunity! \ud83d\ude97 This vehicle is in poor condition \u2014 it has notable wear and mechanical issues that go beyond typical used-car aging, and will require meaningful repairs and attention. That said, it's priced to reflect exactly that, making it a potential fit for a handy buyer or someone looking for an affordable fixer-upper. Come take a look and see if it's the right project for you!",
      "price": 6000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
