      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in good condition \u2014 a dependable used car that has been reasonably well maintained and is ready for everyday driving. The exterior presents well overall, with only minor surface scratches and light wear consistent with normal use; no significant dents or rust to report. The interior is clean and functional, showing some expected wear on high-contact surfaces like the seats and steering wheel, but nothing that detracts from comfort or usability. Mechanically, the car runs reliably with no known major issues, though as with any used vehicle at this price point, buyers should anticipate routine maintenance needs in the near future. All major systems \u2014 engine, transmission, brakes, and HVAC \u2014 are in working order. This is a solid, honest choice for a buyer seeking reliable transportation without paying new-car prices.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in mint condition, and we are proud to present one of the finest examples you will find on the market. The exterior is essentially flawless \u2014 the paint is deep, vibrant, and free of scratches, chips, or fading, with a showroom-quality finish that turns heads. All body panels are perfectly aligned, the trim is intact and pristine, and the glass is crystal clear without any chips or cracks. The interior is equally impressive, showing virtually no signs of wear \u2014 the seats, carpeting, dashboard, and headliner all look and feel as though they have barely been used. Every electronic feature, climate control system, and convenience function operates exactly as intended, with no warning lights or known issues of any kind. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs with smooth, confident power, and the transmission shifts crisply through all gears. The tires have excellent tread remaining and are evenly worn, and the brakes are in excellent working order. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been exceptionally well cared for \u2014 a true mint-condition example that is ready to impress from the moment you take the wheel.",
      "price": 47000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Here's a great opportunity to own a well-maintained vehicle that's ready to impress! This car is in good condition \u2014 it drives smoothly, starts without hesitation, and has been cared for over the years. The interior is clean and comfortable, and the exterior shows only minor signs of normal wear that you'd expect from a responsibly used vehicle. No major mechanical concerns here \u2014 just a dependable, attractive ride at a fair price. If you're looking for quality without the premium price tag of a showroom-fresh car, this one deserves a serious look!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in mint condition \u2014 the highest designation we use, and one we reserve exclusively for cars that genuinely earn it. The exterior is essentially flawless: the paint is deep, rich, and uniform across every panel, with no scratches, chips, swirl marks, or blemishes of any kind. The bodywork is straight and true, the glass is crystal clear, and all trim pieces, badges, and chrome accents are pristine. Step inside and the interior matches that same exceptional standard \u2014 the seats show no wear, the carpets and headliner are spotless, and every surface looks and feels as though the car has barely been used. All controls, buttons, and electronics function exactly as intended, with no quirks or issues to report. Under the hood, the engine is clean and well-maintained, starts immediately, runs smoothly, and pulls strongly through the full rev range. The transmission shifts crisply, the brakes are responsive and even, and the suspension feels tight and composed. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that has been exceptionally well cared for and is ready to deliver a premium ownership experience from day one.",
      "price": 47000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    }
